## ✅ WebSocket vs Socket.IO in React (Interview Topic)

| WebSocket        | Socket.IO      |
| ---------------- | -------------- |
| Protocol         | Library        |
| Lightweight      | Feature‑rich   |
| Manual reconnect | Auto reconnect |
| No fallback      | Has fallback   |
| Low‑level        | High‑level     |

✅ **Socket.IO** = WebSocket + reconnection + rooms + fallback

