## ✅ Common Bugs & Mistakes ⚠️

❌ Creating socket outside `useEffect`  
❌ Forgetting cleanup (memory leaks)  
❌ Recreating socket on every render  
❌ Updating state too frequently (performance issue)

***

## ✅ Performance Tip (Senior‑Level)

For **high‑frequency messages**:

*   Buffer messages
*   Batch updates
*   Use `useReducer`
*   Avoid re-render per message

